These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: january, august, february, may, march, november, july
1. the person who's birthday is in august is in the middle##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left##1
6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Birthday   | july | may | march | august | february | january | november |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-2::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: biathlon, skiing, golf, basketball, rowing, surfing, sailing
1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
6. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |    2    |      3       |   4   |     5     |   6    |    7    |
| Sport   | biathlon | rowing | golf | surfing | basketball | skiing | sailing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-3::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: milk, 7up, cola, sprite, coffee, fanta, lemonade
1. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person drinking cola is in the middle##1
3. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
6. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2      |   3    |    4    |      5      |     6      |    7    |
| Beverage   | coffee | milk | fanta | cola | lemonade | 7up | sprite |

