2. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
3. the fan of disco is on the far right##1
4. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of disco##1
5. the fan of hip-hop is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7    |
| Music-Genre   | pop | salsa | dubstep | hip-hop | r&b | d&b | disco |

