3. the bolivar-smoker is on the far left##1
4. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
5. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
6. the dunhill-smoker is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3   |   4    |   5   |   6    |     7      |
| Cigar   | bolivar | davidoff | siglo | dunhill | tiparillo | vegafina | game |

