.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-20::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: coffee, sprite, juice, fanta, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, mirinda
1. the person drinking coffee is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |    4    |    5    |    6    |    7    |
| Beverage   | fanta | mirinda | iced-tea | coffee | hot-chocolate | juice | sprite |

 